51
00:09:08.212 --> 00:09:11.643
Well. if you want to
be big in America. you would say...?

52
00:09:13.645 --> 00:09:16.246
I'm going to
pass Bruno Mars...

53
00:09:17.513 --> 00:09:18.578
pronto?

54
00:09:18.580 --> 00:09:19.779
Good.

55
00:09:21.346 --> 00:09:22.846
- Let's go.
