what's going on?

70
00:12:52.450 --> 00:12:53.649
Diego...

71
00:12:55.616 --> 00:12:56.747
<i>Si.</i>

72
00:12:56.749 --> 00:12:58.714
I'll go.

73
00:12:58.716 --> 00:13:01.348
