- No. no. no.

74
00:13:10.083 --> 00:13:11.083
Dani Ramos.

75
00:13:16.984 --> 00:13:18.717
How's the game?

76
00:13:41.418 --> 00:13:44.516
Please. Mr. Grummond.
It's my brother.

77
00:13:44.518 --> 00:13:46.884
